{"tid":125792,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"進口老爺車安全帶出牌問題","createTime":"2017-02-18T18:44:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-24T04:04:07.000Z","uid":80498,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2dcabea6e0683d662a869717fd1228ef59573388","tid":125792,"uid":80498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T18:44:12.000Z","msg":"以前有個PO我都講過自己plan緊買AE86<br />\n<br />\n想問一下如果部車本後座身冇安全帶/得兩點式安全帶<br />\n出牌係咪出唔到後座既位?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://picture1.goo-net.com/020/0200600/J/0200600A30170203W00113.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpicture1.goo-net.com%2F020%2F0200600%2FJ%2F0200600A30170203W00113.jpg&h=07175372&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我今日MEGA BOX見部AE86都係寫得一座位+司機位, 佢後面係兩點式安全帶<br />\n<br />\n想問係香港有咩方法可以比運輸署批到後座位?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有聽講過可以焊接條3點式係後坐, 但手續會好煩(聽講要車房同運輸署都要搞好多手續野)同埋用唔少錢<br />\n想問問有冇巴打知道?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想玩車但係又想車埋屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a5bd9bde8cad12c50bef3d49cd960adf9e49efa","tid":125792,"uid":7291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T04:59:49.000Z","msg":"玩咩車人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個頭貼撚住塊玻璃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fbb6b0c7a334c236c8c519f0a02de4d4d19a3dd","tid":125792,"uid":73490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T05:21:24.000Z","msg":"留名 我都想自己入架86返泥 但係冇錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse