","tid":125792,"uid":80498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T06:39:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.legislation.gov.hk/blis_ind.nsf/curallchindoc/8F4AC3E1F8100E7548256EE5002F4600?OpenDocument\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.legislation.gov.hk%2Fblis_ind.nsf%2Fcurallchindoc%2F8F4AC3E1F8100E7548256EE5002F4600%3FOpenDocument&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=0b5496ae\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.legislation.gov.hk/blis_ind.nsf/curallchindoc/8F4AC3E1F8100E7548256EE5002F4600?OpenDocument</a><br />\n<br />\n岩岩搵到，係咪即係叫車房安一條有以上規格既安全帶就OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33bba78cc332f09e7f169481bfac88c439c78f7c","tid":125792,"uid":80498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T01:36:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"594c53e3a084443c1763faf5055445aac88d1c43","tid":125792,"uid":29423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T14:49:40.000Z","msg":"拆左佢加個防滾架算啦"},{"pid":"b3f82eccc9fe02a15fec6092260074cd44580d9a","tid":125792,"uid":39781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:16:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.legislation.gov.hk/blis_ind.nsf/curallchindoc/8F4AC3E1F8100E7548256EE5002F4600?OpenDocument\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.legislation.gov.hk%2Fblis_ind.nsf%2Fcurallchindoc%2F8F4AC3E1F8100E7548256EE5002F4600%3FOpenDocument&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=0b5496ae\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.legislation.gov.hk/blis_ind.nsf/curallchindoc/8F4AC3E1F8100E7548256EE5002F4600?OpenDocument</a><br />\n<br />\n岩岩搵到，係咪即係叫車房安一條有以上規格既安全帶就OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你架車個anchorage point 呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係隨便裝條有E cert既安全帶就得<br />\n隨時要RE做拉力測試去certify個坐位夠磅數，唔會係撞車時飛甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 曾經係車行做過，見識過拉櫈<br />\n<br />\n火炭有檔專做運輸署測試(e.g. 小巴拉櫈)"}]}